data.description: Very Beautiful mid century modern house that sits in a cul-de-sac. With 7 bedrooms and 4 bathrooms, even the Brady Bunch would have had there own rooms.  Kitchen is facing west for evening daylight.  High ceilings give great ambiance as it overlooks the family dining and formal dinning areas.  The  finished bedrooms in the basement can be removed to add an additional family room or keep more space for guest rooms and/or cozy sleep ins.  Concrete tile roof for your family's safety during wind and hail months in Colorado.  Home is located in a highly desirable quite neighborhood with mature trees. Many lavish homes through out the subdivision and others well about 1 million also.  Easy commute in and around Lakewood and Bow Mar.  All measurements are approximate, buyer to verify.
